frames.caption: A white cat dressed in a traditional kimono sits gracefully on a stone by a tranquil stream. Surrounding the cat are blooming cherry blossoms, with a red arched bridge in the background. The scene is serene and picturesque, evoking a sense of peace and beauty.
frames.description: The scene depicts a tranquil setting in a Japanese garden during cherry blossom season. A cat wearing a kimono is the focal point, surrounded by pink cherry blossoms and a red bridge over a stream.
